rComments: This class is awful, the professor is boring and unhelpful and belligerent. The textbook is even worse but of course, he wrote it!  I am a textbook learner and it's virtually impossible to learn from it.  The appendix also sucks.

This professor should retire.  He is an old, grouchy guy who is not very helpful.  He loves to give you tons of reading and exams are monster sized.  He makes you never want to ask him questions.  Should not be teaching.  BAD, BAD
